{"tid":180094,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"真心一問(勁苦惱)","createTime":"2017-03-30T16:46:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-31T03:03:04.000Z","uid":19100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7ebc6e92d3ec22a063349153619f6475d5859b71","tid":180094,"uid":19100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T16:46:08.000Z","msg":"&lt;借朋友ac&gt;<br />\n有無人知點解啲玻璃膠會咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一年前租呢個單位，幾個月前開始有白色粒粒出現，廁所窗黎，日日都長開抽氣扇，個廁所每日都抹，基本上個廁所好乾爽，其他位置玻璃膠無發霉無黑色一點點。<br />\n業主屈9我地污糟，淨係叫我地要定時清潔，唔肯處理，但屋企人早晚都會吸塵拖地，屋企真心唔污糟，有無人知可以點做🙏🏻🙏🏻🙏🏻<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/196d9Fm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F196d9Fm.jpg&h=8a12e696&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a38HuLd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa38HuLd.jpg&h=fc16f3b8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9665d75fe1ee879345d8cc52a09ed4be444c20be","tid":180094,"uid":5006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T22:46:07.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"d71bd53f83503465740691157bc3e2dc41555bea","tid":180094,"uid":19100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T03:03:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}